1
00:00:09,968 --> 00:00:13,370
intervyu mit MONSIUR Hershkovitsh, ferte kaset.

2
00:00:13,512 --> 00:00:16,611
MONSIUR Hershkovitsh, vilt ir aykh forshteln ayer froy?

3
00:00:16,684 --> 00:00:19,749
dos iz mayn froy biz hundert un tsvontsik yor,

4
00:00:20,975 --> 00:00:23,681
Freyde Rifke Shteymets heyst zi,

5
00:00:23,755 --> 00:00:26,314
undz ho'mir tsu gutn khasene gehat ven?

6
00:00:28,125 --> 00:00:33,201
tsvey un tsvontsik, un un dos resht, zog zog du oykh a bisl!

7
00:00:33,226 --> 00:00:34,603
vu hot ir khasene gehat?

8
00:00:36,759 --> 00:00:38,676
ir hot aykh bagegnt oykhet in Yisroel?

9
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:40,800
undz ho'mir zikh kenen gelernt in Yisroel.

10
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:42,380
un khasene gehat in Yisroel.

11
00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:44,100
un nokh dem,

12
00:00:44,474 --> 00:00:50,681
un kinder ho'mir in Belgyen gehat, a- dray kinder ho'mir, zoln zayn gezunt un shtark,

13
00:00:50,873 --> 00:00:52,993
un fir eyniklekh.

14
00:00:53,877 --> 00:00:57,240
un di eyniklekh zenen ale geboyrn

15
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,999
in Yisroel, un di kinder zenen do geboyrn.

16
00:00:59,999 --> 00:01:01,509
tsvey kinder

17
00:01:01,509 --> 00:01:06,729
mit di eyniklekh voynen in Yisroel un eyn zun voynt do.

18
00:01:07,191 --> 00:01:09,227
vilst,

19
00:01:09,385 --> 00:01:16,432
ir vilt epes zogn madam Hershkovitsh vegn di SHOAH, tsi s'hot gehat epes a efekt oyf ayer man tsi oyf ayer lebn tsi...

20
00:01:16,455 --> 00:01:19,741
epes vos hot a shaykhes dertsu.

21
00:01:40,179 --> 00:01:44,158
m'hot mikh gefregt tsi ikh hob gezen Shindler's Liste,

22
00:01:44,434 --> 00:01:55,734
iz farshtendlekh ikh hob gezen di televizye ven m'hot es getsaygt ayngezagt, ober geyn kukn bin ikh nisht gegangen kukn, vayl ikh hob gezogt ikh vil nisht nokh a mol iberlebn.

23
00:01:56,213 --> 00:01:57,861
un tsveytns,

24
00:01:57,883 --> 00:02:03,597
ikh bin aleyn an an artist gevezn dort in film,

25
00:02:12,818 --> 00:02:18,837
ober ven di rusn kumen dray tog shpeter, volt men zey yo deportirt, nor zenen gekumen,

26
00:02:23,766 --> 00:02:26,429
un zenen arayngekumen dray tog frier di rusn,

27
00:02:29,757 --> 00:02:32,677
un vos s'hot zikh getun, yo.

28
00:02:56,608 --> 00:03:01,445
di SHOAH hot gehat a epes a oysvirkung oyf ayer religyez lebn oykhet?

29
00:03:03,713 --> 00:03:04,432
neyn.

30
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,470
nisht aroyf un nisht arunter.

31
00:03:09,396 --> 00:03:10,256
nokh dem.

32
00:03:11,965 --> 00:03:14,473
ikh bin mitgegangen mitn vint.

33
00:03:17,736 --> 00:03:22,151
un ikh halt az m'tor nisht tsu fil araynklern.

34
00:03:23,845 --> 00:03:25,408
m'hot gefregt a yid,

35
00:03:25,617 --> 00:03:29,087
a groysn talmed-khokhem nokhn krig, hot yemolt mir gezogt,

36
00:03:29,346 --> 00:03:30,892
az m'hot im gefregt,

37
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,777
vos

38
00:03:32,777 --> 00:03:36,596
vos zogt ir tsu dem vos hot pasirt, un azoy vayter,

39
00:03:36,906 --> 00:03:42,654
hot er, un yener iz geven a groyser talmed-khokhem, zogt er, ikh hob tsu veynik gelernt ikh zol dos kenen erklern.

40
00:03:45,951 --> 00:03:48,681
s'iz nokh epes do vos ir vilt zogn MONSIUR Hershkovitsh?

41
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:51,466
a gutn shabes.

42
00:03:48,681 --> 00:03:49,297
far di,

43
00:03:56,430 --> 00:04:00,103
PREFER UNE AUTRE LANGUE, yidish iz gut, neyn?

44
